// News Section
section.py-5
  .container
    h1.text-center.mb-5 Latest News and Updates
    .row
      // News Article 1: Liverpool's Latest Victory
      .col-md-4
        .card.mb-4
          img.card-img-top(src='images/WhatsApp Image 2024-11-18 at 11.32.40_22383707.jpg' alt="Liverpool's Latest Victory")
          .card-body
            h5.card-title Liverpool&apos;s Latest Victory
            p.card-text
              | Liverpool&apos;s recent 2-1 win against Chelsea saw them regain the top spot in the Premier League. Mohamed Salah scored a penalty and assisted Curtis Jones for the decisive goal.
            a.btn.btn-danger(href='https://www.skysports.com/liverpool-results') Read More
      // News Article 2: Transfer Rumors: Who's Next?
      .col-md-4
        .card.mb-4
          img.card-img-top(src='images/WhatsApp Image 2024-11-18 at 11.32.02_e22f0e31.jpg' alt='Transfer Rumors')
          .card-body
            h5.card-title Transfer Rumors: Who&apos;s Next?
            p.card-text
              | Liverpool is eyeing young talent Arda G&uuml;ler from Real Madrid to strengthen their midfield. The club is also exploring defensive reinforcements.
            a.btn.btn-danger(href='https://www.skysports.com/football/transfer-news') Read More
      // News Article 3: Upcoming Fixtures and Previews
      .col-md-4
        .card.mb-4
          img.card-img-top(src='images/WhatsApp Image 2024-11-18 at 11.41.55_04e653ee.jpg' alt='Upcoming Fixtures')
          .card-body
            h5.card-title Upcoming Fixtures and Previews
            p.card-text
              | Liverpool faces key matches, including a Champions League clash against RB Leipzig and a Premier League showdown with Arsenal.
            a.btn.btn-danger(href='https://www.liverpoolfc.com/fixtures/mens/2024') Read More
    .row
      // News Article 4: Fan Stories: Ugandan Reds in Action
      .col-md-4
        .card.mb-4
          img.card-img-top(src='images/WhatsApp Image 2024-11-18 at 11.30.57_ed16176f.jpg' alt='Ugandan Reds')
          .card-body
